= XQuery Examples Collection =
'''Welcome to the XQuery Examples Collection Wikibook!'''
XQuery is a [[w:W3C|World Wide Web Consortium]] [[w:W3C_recommendation|recommendation]] for selecting data from documents and databases.

== Current Status ==

We are in the process of testing many of these examples using the eXist 2.0 release.  Please let us know if you find any problems.  We are looking for volunteers to help us create XQuery 3.0 examples.

[[Special:Recentchangeslinked/XQuery | Recent Changes]]

